node.text:
BIG INVENTORY HEADS UP 😷 

@baggu has stopped wholesale selling of masks to retailers, it's utterly heartbreaking as these were our favorite masks and we know how much our customers loved them. That being said. What is in stock is the last of our inventory, we weren't given any notice and therefore were not able to stock up as we would have liked. 

Head to the site and scoop up what is left, there's a fair amount of kids + adult sets but this is it! 

If you have another favorite brand of adult + kids masks let us know in the comments, we are considering adding another brand in it's place. We do also have adult + kids tie dye mask sets in stock as well.

node.text:
Community Fundraising Project 🕊🗳 

We are happy to share we've restocked button packs + added a brand new 'Good Citizen Button + Sticker Pack' to the site. These raise awareness + funds for orgs we love

Tees + Vote Button Packs (a portion of the profits) + BLM Packs (100% of profits) to @blackvotersmtr 

Good Citizen Packs - a portion of the profits going to @aclu_nationwide 

We will have a HUGE restock of Your Voice Your Vote Tees for Holiday (and again next year as we lead to the midterms) but for now we've got the following kids sizes (on sale too!):

3-6m
6-12m
12-18m
18-24m
2Y
4Y
6Y
10Y

Thank you for your support in these fundraising projects. We love being able to have the platform to do this and it's because of you we can. 

Xx - Lindsay

I listed adult + kids sizes in the shop along with a HUGE @baggu mask restock 👏🏼 grab em while they’re there, not sure how long we’ll be making them 😉 

ps. If you have color requests let us know in the comments and will do our best to accommodate
